    "description": {
      "value": "<p>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.Fim0r8kwu9pO2qPe]{Weapon Group: Small Arms, Two-Handed}</p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">The weapon is a sleek, smooth, multi-piece item of black and silver, constructed from polymer and carbon fiber. The weapon is less clumsy than ancient designs.&nbsp;<br></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">The carbon crossbow comes with a range finding scope. Use a bonus action to aim with the scope, nullifying the disadvantage of firing long range.</span></p>\n<table class=\"NormalTable\" style=\"height: 85px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 85px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 85px; width: 59px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Carbon Crossbow </span></td>\n<td style=\"height: 85px; width: 40px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">500uc </span></td>\n<td style=\"height: 85px; width: 88px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">1d10 piercing </span></td>\n<td style=\"height: 85px; width: 32px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">6 lb. </span></td>\n<td style=\"height: 85px; width: 168px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Ammunition (range 200/600), heavy, loading, two-handed</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.N5tzQ0cKBbaU25Qs]{Ammunition}&nbsp;@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.aHgsBOaLpXxmywsG]{Heavy}&nbsp;@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.C6LUHCPzyZBU7dA5]{Two-Handed}</p>",
